Description: Fragment of plain weave and tapestry; one central medallion with human figure (running?); this is surrounded with a solid wavy line with stylised interlacing and dots; plain weave: warp-undyed wool (S/11), weft-undyed wool (S/above the medallion is single at 24, below the medallion is irregular single and paired threads); tapestry on single threads: warp-undyed wool (S/11), weft-bleached wool (S/56), purple wool (S/68); all edges cut or ragged
